		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;143&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;345px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;叶片全局坐标系&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/iec-61400-23%E5%8F%B6%E7%89%87%E5%85%A8%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB/image-20251105163057769.png&#34;
